title: CRAFT MATES Bead Organizer and Plastic Storage Containers for Crafts, Buttons, Pins and More, 56 Locking Compartments, Clear Lids
description: Large storage case lets you take your crafting components with you. Organize all your jewelry, beads, sequins, needles, buttons, scrapbooking items and more in this pretty purple case. The patented lock-bar allows you to open one clear compartment at a time. Details: Purple faux suede carrying case snaps closed. Case holds 56 locking compartments. Patented lock-bar allows you to open one compartment at a time. Contents: Double-sided carrying case 8 plastic Lockables Organizers (2XL).
